{"prompt": "Develop a site for a residential roofing service. The design should be trustworthy, with a safety yellow accent.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Reliable Roofs - Your Trusted Roofing Experts</title>\n    <style>\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: #f4f7f6;\n            color: #333;\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n        .container {\n            width: 80%;\n            margin: auto;\n            overflow: hidden;\n            padding: 30px 0;\n        }\n        header {\n            background: #34495e; /* Dark, trustworthy blue-grey */\n            color: #ecf0f1; /* Light grey for text */\n            padding-top: 30px;\n            min-height: 70px;\n            border-bottom: #f39c12 3px solid; /* Safety yellow accent */\n        }\n        header h1 {\n            text-align: center;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding-bottom: 10px;\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n            letter-spacing: 1px;\n        }\n        #hero {\n            background: linear-gradient(rgba(52, 73, 94, 0.7), rgba(52, 73, 94, 0.7)), url('https://via.placeholder.com/1500x800/34495e/ffffff?text=Beautiful+Roof+Image') no-repeat center center/cover;\n            height: 500px;\n            text-align: center;\n            color: #fff;\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n            justify-content: center;\n            align-items: center;\n            border-bottom: #f39c12 5px solid; /* Safety yellow accent */\n        }\n        #hero h2 {\n            margin-top: 0;\n            font-size: 3em;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);\n        }\n        #hero p {\n            font-size: 1.3em;\n  